@startuml
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam nodesep 100
skinparam ranksep 100
title Accounting Archetype - Core Concept

' ===== GŁÓWNE KONCEPTY =====

object Account {
  accountId: AccountId
  type: AccountType
  name: AccountName
  balance: Money
  --
  addEntry(entry)
  balance(): Money
}

object "Entry\n<<sealed>>" as Entry {
  id: EntryId
  transactionId: TransactionId
  accountId: AccountId
  amount: Money
  occurredAt: Instant
  appliesAt: Instant
  metadata: MetaData
  validity: Validity
}

object AccountDebited {
  amount negated
}

object AccountCredited {
  amount positive
}

object Transaction {
  id: TransactionId
  type: TransactionType
  entries: Map<Account, List<Entry>>
  --
  execute()
}

object "TransactionEntriesConstraint\n<<interface>>" as TransactionEntriesConstraint {
  errorMessage(): String
  test(entries): boolean
  isApplicable(entries): boolean
}

object BALANCING_CONSTRAINT {
  Σ amounts = 0
}

object MIN_2_ENTRIES_CONSTRAINT {
  entries.size() >= 2
}

object MIN_2_ACCOUNTS_INVOLVED_CONSTRAINT {
  accounts.size() >= 2
}

object "PostingRule\n<<interface>>" as PostingRule {
  isEligible(context): boolean
  execute(context): List<Transaction>
}

' ===== RELACJE =====

Transaction "1" *--> "2..*" Entry : contains
Transaction --> TransactionEntriesConstraint : validates
Entry --> Account : debit OR credit

AccountDebited -up-|> Entry
AccountCredited -up-|> Entry

BALANCING_CONSTRAINT -up-|> TransactionEntriesConstraint
MIN_2_ENTRIES_CONSTRAINT -up-|> TransactionEntriesConstraint
MIN_2_ACCOUNTS_INVOLVED_CONSTRAINT -up-|> TransactionEntriesConstraint

PostingRule ..> Transaction : triggered by\ngenerates more

note right of Account
  **Account = Konto księgowe**

  AccountType (enum):
  - ASSET (majątek)
  - LIABILITY (zobowiązania)
  - EXPENSE (koszty)
  - REVENUE (przychody)
  - OFF_BALANCE (pozabilansowe)

  ✓ NIE wie o właścicielach!
  ✓ Tylko księgowanie
  ✓ Optimistic locking (version)
end note

note left of Transaction
  **Transaction = Transakcja**

  Grupuje entries
  (double-entry bookkeeping)

  **Walidacja przez Constraints:**
  - BALANCING_CONSTRAINT
  - MIN_2_ENTRIES_CONSTRAINT
  - MIN_2_ACCOUNTS_INVOLVED_CONSTRAINT

  refId = referencja dla reversals
  execute() = dodaje entries do kont
end note

note bottom of Entry
  **Entry = Sealed interface**

  **AccountDebited:**
  amount().negate() (ujemna)

  **AccountCredited:**
  amount (dodatnia)

  **appliedTo:**
  Optional<EntryId> - alokacja
  do innego entry

  **validity:**
  okres ważności zapisu
end note

note top of PostingRule
  **Posting Rule = Automatyzacja**

  Na podstawie Transaction
  generuje dodatkowe Transactions

  **ConfigurablePostingRule:**
  - eligibilityCondition
  - accountFinder
  - calculator
  - priority
end note

@enduml
